com.robinpowered.sdk.model

Class Event

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.robinpowered.sdk.model.Event
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ApiResponseModel, IdentifiableApiResponseModel, Serializable

    public class Event
extends Object
implements IdentifiableApiResponseModel
    A meeting or reservation, booked in a Space.

    While Presence represents the current state of who is within a space, an event is a pre-booked reservation for a space that multiple people may be invited to.

    Events are often synchronized from an external calendar service, such as Google Calendar or Office 365. Events may also be created by booking a Space through Robin.
